    "answer_id" : 35111885,
    "question_id" : 10631715,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can split it and make an array then access like an array:</p>\n<pre><code>String names = &quot;prappo,prince&quot;;\nString[] namesList = names.split(&quot;,&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can access it with its indexes</p>\n<pre><code>String name1 = namesList [0];\nString name2 = namesList [1];\n</code></pre>\n<p>or using a loop</p>\n<pre><code>for(String name : namesList){\n    System.out.println(name);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
