    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>in build.gradle add Guava </p>\n\n<pre><code>    compile group: 'com.google.guava', name: 'guava', version: '27.0-jre'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and then</p>\n\n<pre><code>    public static List&lt;String&gt; splitByComma(String str) {\n    Iterable&lt;String&gt; split = Splitter.on(\",\")\n            .omitEmptyStrings()\n            .trimResults()\n            .split(str);\n    return Lists.newArrayList(split);\n    }\n\n    public static String joinWithComma(Set&lt;String&gt; words) {\n        return Joiner.on(\", \").skipNulls().join(words);\n    }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>enjoy :)</p>\n"
