    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>This is an easy way to split string by comma,</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>import java.util.*;\n\npublic class SeparatedByComma{\npublic static void main(String []args){\n     String listOfStates = \"Hasalak, Mahiyanganaya, Dambarawa, Colombo\";\n     List&lt;String&gt; stateList = Arrays.asList(listOfStates.split(\"\\\\,\"));\n     System.out.println(stateList);\n }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2204985,
      "reputation" : 1250,
      "user_id" : 1948438,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/aade09a6fae8bf51c14c71ddb8f9469c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "CamelTM",
