    "body" : "<p>Easy and Short solution:-</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>String str=&quot;test 1 ,test 2  , test 3&quot;;</p>\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; elementList = Arrays.asList(str.replaceAll(&quot;\\\\s*,\\\\s*&quot;, &quot;,&quot;).split(&quot;,&quot;));\n</code></pre>\n<p>Output=[&quot;test 1&quot;,&quot;test 2&quot;,&quot;test 3&quot;]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It will working for all cases.</p>\n<p>Thanks me later :-)</p>\n"
